Armorial of the Norman and the Audenhove
Azure from the sable to the chief, with the whole strewn with gold bars; a lion also gold, armed and langued gules, standing on the bars.
<span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 13px;">&laquo; <span style="font-size: 16px; caret-color: #212529; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; font-style: italic; text-align: center;">De sable au chef cousu d'azur, le tout sem&eacute; de billettes d'or ; au lion aussi d'or, arm&eacute; et lampass&eacute; de gueules, brochant sur les billettes.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; font-size: 13px;">&raquo;

